<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=99158490358076></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f99158490358076><tr><td id=headerrow><span id=sj><a href=/strategy/classes.html?class=4&mid=99158490358076>RE: money</a></span></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Sun, Jun 3rd 12:15 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Well thats about the best way to make money at your lvl, i would run around to vendors and buy all the bone chips off of them, sell them for 5pp a stack (20).  Im sure if someone has given you a better weapon than bronze at 9 that your doing good also, you are still very young, however as far as armour goes, save up about 30-35pp and get you some banded made from a master smith, usually sells for 1pp an AC, don't pay anymore than that.<br>Also depending on where your at continue to fight, get up to lvl 15 and head over to High Hold pass and get into gnoll group, the polished granite tomahawk drops there and cracked darkwood shield, that will be good weapon for your lvl and sheild or sell them PGT around 95pp, CDS 200pp.  Take care and happy hunting, work for all your equip thats the fun of the game, just my 2cp.  Happy Hunting<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
