<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=99072193451295></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f99072193451295><tr><td id=headerrow><span id=sj><a href=/strategy/classes.html?class=4&mid=99072193451295>lvl 17 to 27 easy and good xp</a></span></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?id=49059><span id= >Valaba</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>4 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Thu, May 24th 12:32 PM 2001</td>
