	   <tr><td colspan=2>ok i haven't done this myself...but you havta talk to banker in FV to start the quest. he wants the Star of Odus, bought in Erudin for 100 some pp. give that to him and he'll give you a container to combine the coins in. use your cataloging song to identify the coins by picking the coins up so it appears on your cursor then start the song and it'll tell you the name of the coin. the names and where they drop are:<br><br>-Ik Gran Coin - drops off the Captain of the Guard in the City of Mist<br>-Terraz Ton Coin - drops off the Failed Raider in Kaesora<br>-Danak Gran Coin - drops off the Scrounger Scorpion in the Overthere<br>-Veksar Gran Coin - drops off the Bloodgill Goblins in the Lake the Ill Omen<br>-Royal Crown of Dalnir Coin - drops off the Kly Implicator in Dalnir<br>-Torsis Ton Coin - foraged coin in the Emerald Jungle<br><br>once you place all the coins in the container and hit combine, give the resulting item back to the banker and you'll receive Nostrolo's Tambourine. its magic, lore and no drop which goes in secondary hand slot like your regular instruments. it weighs only .5 and adds +5 to int, also a 25% increase to percussion songs (bout 5% more than MM drums).<br><br>have fun<br><br>Taamas Starsinger<br>40th Season<br>House of Wargoth<br>Saryrn<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
