	   <tr><td colspan=2>im pretty sure he/she means disciplines...the ones you havta use the /disc command for, heres they are:<br><br>lvl 54 - Fearless - Makes you immune to fear spells for 11 secs. Reuse time of 1 hr.<br><br>lvl 55 - Deftdance - Activates Auto Dodge and Dual Wield for 15 secs (no idea what that means sorry). Reuse time of 72 mins.<br><br>lvl 60 - Puretone - Adds bonuses to all songs, just like the best instrument were being used, which lasts for 4 mins. Reuse time of 72 mins.<br><br>this is all from www.eqdiva.com a great bard site  =)<br><br>Taamas Starsinger<br>40th Season<br>House of Wargoth<br>Saryrn<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
